    "body": "Hi @holiman just to understand better, PBSS will then be more space efficient but node operators still need to run offline pruning? (i.e.: eventually/less often). If so, do you foresee any changes on how to perform offline pruning (this [doc](https://geth.ethereum.org/docs/fundamentals/pruning))?\r\n\r\nFor context, we're evaluating if it's worth automate the pruning process. But if PBSS changes that, we might wait or choose not to do it.",
